c: 8
v: 36
t: Bila shak yeh kafir log apne maalon ko iss liye kharch ker rahey hain kay Allah ki raah say roken so yeh lo to apney maalon ko kharach kertay hi rahen gay phir woh maal inn kay haq mein baees-e-hasrat hojayen gay. Phir maghloob hojayen gay aur kafir logon ko dozakh ki taraf jama kiya jayega